This Mother’s Day, bring a smile on her face!

Join us this Sunday at Club Fenicia for ‘Brunch to Drunch’ and an exuberant day filled with laughter, joy, warmth and an appreciation towards all the mothers out there for their invaluable contributions in every sphere of our lives!.

Shower love on  all the  beautiful  mothers and treat her like the ultimate queen!

Event Details

Date: May 11th, 2025

Time: 12 p.m. onwards 

Venue: Club Fenicia (10th Floor, TOWER-1, GODREJ WATERSIDE, DP Block, Sector V, Bidhannagar, Kolkata, West Bengal 700091)

Highlights of the event:

Enjoy a lavish & scrumptious buffet at INR 1299/-

Experience a live music performance

Take home special giveaways

Participate in exciting games

The stage is set for all mothers to have a gala time and feel extra special!

See you  at Club Fenicia this Sunday to celebrate motherhood and an exceptional Mother’s Day!
